1. *Brinete* se previše oko sitnica. (You worry too much about trivial things.)
2. *Brinete* li se za svoje zdravlje? (Do you care about your health?)
3. Ona *brine* o deci kao da su joj sopstvena. (She cares for children as if they were her own.)
4. Da li ćete mi *brinuti* kuću dok sam na odmoru? (Will you take care of my house while I'm on vacation?)
5. Ova krema *brine* o hidrataciji kože. (This cream takes care of skin hydration.)
6. Kako se *brinuti* o kućnim ljubimcima tokom leta. (How to take care of pets during summer.)
7. Sestra *brine* o starijim roditeljima dok se brat bavi poslom. (Sister takes care of elderly parents while brother is at work.)
8. *Brinete* li se da će vas neko videti? (Are you worried that someone will see you?)
9. Mladi roditelji se *brinu* o finansijskoj sigurnosti svoje porodice. (Young parents are worried about the financial security of their family.)
10. Preduzeće se *brine* o zaštiti životne sredine. (The company takes care of environmental protection.)